<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<%- include('./partials/head.ejs') %>

<body>
    
    <%- include('./partials/nav.ejs') %>
    
    <div class="about content">

    <section class="about-hero">
        <h1>About Blogify</h1>
        <p>
            Welcome to <strong>Blogify</strong>, a place where ideas turn into
            stories and stories connect people.
        </p>
    </section>


    <section class="about-section">

        <h2>Our Mission</h2>

        <p>
            We believe every person has a story worth sharing. Blogify makes it
            easy for users to write blogs, express their opinions, and explore
            different perspectives from a community of writers.
        </p>

    </section>


    <section class="about-section">

        <h2>What You Can Do</h2>

        <div class="features">

            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>✍️ Create Blogs</h3>
                <p>
                    Write and publish your own blogs with your ideas,
                    experiences, and knowledge.
                </p>
            </div>


            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>📖 Read Stories</h3>
                <p>
                    Discover interesting stories and thoughts from different
                    writers.
                </p>
            </div>


            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>🖼️ Add Images</h3>
                <p>
                    Make your blogs more engaging by adding images to your
                    stories.
                </p>
            </div>


            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>🌎 Share Ideas</h3>
                <p>
                    Share your creativity and connect with a wider audience.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>

    </section>


    <section class="about-section">

        <h2>Why Blogify?</h2>

        <p>
            We designed Blogify with simplicity in mind. Whether you are a
            beginner writer or an experienced blogger, our platform provides a
            clean and user-friendly environment to focus on what matters most —
            your content.
        </p>

    </section>


    <section class="about-cta">

        <h2>Join Our Community</h2>

        <p>
            Start writing, sharing, and discovering new ideas with Blogify.
            Your next story could inspire someone.
        </p>

        <h3>Write. Share. Inspire.</h3>

    </section>

</div>
    
     <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>